{"article_id":"3q4oCOSRctpVjQ7F","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The second enrollment period at HealthCare.gov began Saturday ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"and so far , it 's gone much more smoothly than the start of last year 's first open enrollment ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"which was full of glitches","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and saw only a handful of people able to enroll the first day .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The Department of Health and Human Services said","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"that on Saturday alone , more than 100,000 people applied for healthcare on the site ,","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"and more than half a million people logged on .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"NPR 's Elise Hu previously reported","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"that the healthcare.gov","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"users are seeing this weekend","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"is a substantially faster , better website","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"that it was last year :","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Its load times have improved substantially ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and the administration says","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"it can handle twice as much traffic volume as last year .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"For customers","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"shopping for coverage ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"you actually browse plans","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"- get a sense of what they cost ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"check eligibility for tax credits ...","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and decide","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"whether you want to buy .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Hu also found","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"that the site has a new system in place","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"to detect traffic overloads faster ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"and programmers from the Department of Homeland Security are trying to hack the site","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"to make sure","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"it 's safe .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Health and Human Services Secretary Sylvia Burwell went on NBC 's Meet The Press Sunday","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"the website works .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"`` I think","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"the vast majority of people","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"coming to the site","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"were able to get on","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"and do what they were intending to do , ''","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"said Burwell .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"But she admitted","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"even as the number of Americans","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"without health insurance","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"continues to drop ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and as more Americans began to take advantage of some of the benefits of the Affordable Care Act ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"lots of Americans are still dissatisfied with the law .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"`` I think","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"one of the things","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"we need to do","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"is translate that success , ''","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"said Burwell .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"`` Because I think","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"when you ask the American people about those things individually ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"or when you ask the American people about the importance","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"of no longer being held off healthcare","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"because of preexisting conditions ,","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"or the fact","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"that their children up to the age 26 can be on their plans ...","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"When you ask them about the substance of the issue ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"the American people respond positively .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"And that 's what I think","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"we need to do more about . ''","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Polling on the ACA continues to find","depth":3},{"id":61,"text":"that about half of Americans have negative feelings about the law ,","depth":4},{"id":62,"text":"though people","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"who enroll in plans through government exchanges","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"are generally satisfied with their coverage .","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"Meanwhile , comments","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"made by one of the architects of the law","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"continues to draw criticism .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"Video recently surfaced of MIT economist Jonathan Gruber","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"the `` stupidity of the American voter '' helped get the law passed .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"The Obama administration has already distanced itself from Gruber 's statements ,","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"and Republicans are strongly condemning the remarks .","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"But that might be less of a problem for the ACA than the new Congress ,","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"which will have both chambers controlled by Republicans in its new term .","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Several members of the party say","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"repealing Obamacare will be their first order of business .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":136,"right":152,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":83,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":80,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":0,"right":79,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":79,"left":1,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":82,"left":4,"right":81,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":81,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":135,"left":103,"right":134,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":97,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"}